    <p><strong>Loreen Siana</strong> presents <em>Human to Tech</em>â€”a project exploring the close integration between humans and technology. Our rapid technological evolution, especially in AI, raises questions: Are we advancing into a future of augmented capabilities or stepping into unprecedented challenges? This project invites you to share your perspective and helps build a data-driven understanding of our collective sentiment toward technological integration.</p>
    <p>By participating in our survey, you contribute to an evolving database that will be analyzed over time. Our aim is to encourage thoughtful dialogue and informed decisions about the future of AI and human augmentation.</p>
